---
import MainLayout from "@/components/layout/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Read the Small Web Apps privacy overview and how browser-first tools handle your data."
  canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
  <section class="static-page">
    <div class="static-inner">
      <span class="static-eyebrow">Privacy</span>
      <h1>A browser-first privacy posture,<br/>explained plainly</h1>
      <div class="static-card">
        <p><strong>Browser-Based Processing</strong></p>
        <p>Small Web Apps focuses on lightweight browser-based utilities. Tool inputs are processed in the browser unless a tool page clearly says otherwise.</p>
        <p>We do not run accounts, paywalls, or server-side file uploads for the tools. Some site-level services may still receive standard web request data, such as IP address, browser information, referrer, and page URL.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 16px;"><strong>Advertising & Analytics</strong></p>
        <p>If advertising or analytics is enabled, Google AdSense and related vendors may serve personalized or non-personalized ads based on your browsing history and interests. Third-party vendors (including Google) use cookies and similar technologies to deliver these ads.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 16px;"><strong>Third-Party Cookies & Tracking</strong></p>
        <p>Google AdSense and other advertising partners may place cookies on your browser to:</p>
        <ul style="margin: 8px 0 0 20px; padding: 0;">
          <li style="margin: 6px 0;">Deliver targeted ads based on your visit history</li>
          <li style="margin: 6px 0;">Track ad performance and conversions</li>
          <li style="margin: 6px 0;">Prevent click fraud and other abuse</li>
          <li style="margin: 6px 0;">Show personalized ads when you visit other sites</li>
        </ul>

        <p style="margin-top: 16px;"><strong>Cookie Types Used When Ads Are Enabled</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin: 8px 0 0 20px; padding: 0;">
          <li style="margin: 6px 0;"><strong>Advertising cookies:</strong> Placed by Google AdSense and ad networks to serve personalized ads</li>
          <li style="margin: 6px 0;"><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Track site usage and user behavior (if Google Analytics is enabled)</li>
          <li style="margin: 6px 0;"><strong>Consent cookies:</strong> Remember your choice from the cookie banner (accept or decline)</li>
        </ul>

        <p style="margin-top: 16px;"><strong>Control Personalized Ads</strong></p>
        <p>You can control how Google and other advertisers use your data:</p>
        <ul style="margin: 8px 0 0 20px; padding: 0;">
          <li style="margin: 6px 0;"><a class="prose-link" href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ad Preferences</a> — View and manage your interests; opt out of personalized ads</li>
          <li style="margin: 6px 0;"><a class="prose-link" href="https://optout.networkadvertising.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Network Advertising Initiative (NAI)</a> — Opt out of interest-based ads from NAI members</li>
          <li style="margin: 6px 0;"><a class="prose-link" href="https://optout.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Digital Advertising Alliance (DAA)</a> — Use the WebChoice tool to control personalized ads</li>
        </ul>

        <p style="margin-top: 16px;"><strong>Site-Level Privacy</strong></p>
        <p>This privacy page is a site-level overview. Each app page remains responsible for accurately describing its own data handling and limitations.</p>
        <div class="static-highlight">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          <p>Private tool content, such as pasted text or selected files, is handled locally by browser-based tools unless the specific tool page states a network dependency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
.static-page {
  max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 24px 80px;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
}
.static-inner { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
.static-eyebrow {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
  background: rgba(26,115,232,.1); color: var(--blue);
  padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 20px;
  font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .1em;
  width: fit-content;
}
h1 {
  font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem); font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -.5px; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0;
}
.static-card {
  background: var(--surface-strong); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}
.static-card p {
  font-size: .95rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--muted); margin: 0;
}
.static-highlight {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
  background: rgba(26,115,232,.07); border: 1px solid rgba(26,115,232,.15);
  border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 18px; margin-top: 8px;
  color: var(--blue);
}
.static-highlight svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
.static-highlight p  { color: var(--blue) !important; font-weight: 500; font-size: .88rem !important; line-height: 1.6 !important; }
</style>
